OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FDame Esther Rantzen's daughter said
OL,7,Fshe is "furious" with the House of
OL,8,FLords, accusing it of blocking the
OL,9,Fassisted dying bill.
OL,11,FSpeaking at a demonstration in
OL,12,FParliament Square on Wednesday in
OL,13,Fsupport of a change in the law,
OL,14,FRebecca Wilcox said her terminally ill
OL,15,Fmother wished she could have attended.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@PO]
