OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FThe Terminally Ill Adults (End of
OL,7,FLife) Bill, which proposed legalising
OL,8,Fassisted dying in England and Wales,
OL,9,Fis expected to fall at the end of
OL,10,FFriday's debate, its final scheduled
OL,11,Fsitting of this session of Parliament.
OL,13,FIt had proposed allowing adults in
OL,14,FEngland and Wales with fewer than six
OL,15,Fmonths to live to apply for an
OL,16,Fassisted death, subject to the
OL,17,Fapproval of two doctors and an expert
OL,18,Fpanel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FIt has had more than 1,000 amendments
OL,7,Fproposed by peers in the Lords `
OL,8,Fbelieved to be a record high number
OL,9,Ffor a piece of backbench legislation.
OL,11,FIt is understood the final debate on
OL,12,FFriday is likely to focus on the
OL,13,Fprocess and how the Bill has run out
OL,14,Fof time, rather than continued
OL,15,Fdiscussion on its contents.
OL,17,FMs Wilcox said: "This delay, this lack
OL,18,Fof a vote, this lack of choice has a
OL,19,Freal human cost.
OL,26,@yD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,F"It's really a sea of warmth and pink
OL,7,Fand smiling and loveliness here today,
OL,8,Fbut I can't help feeling unbelievably
OL,9,Ffurious that we are here again when we
OL,10,Fshould be celebrating a vote."
OL,12,FDame Esther, 85, was diagnosed with
OL,13,Fterminal lung cancer in January 2023,
OL,14,Fand has since been a leading voice in
OL,15,Fthe campaign to legalise assisted
OL,16,Fdying.
OL,18,FThe Childline founder and former
OL,19,Fbroadcaster has previously urged the
OL,20,FHouse of Lords not to "try and
OL,21,Fsabotage democracy".
OL,26,@nD@AO]rD@^O]|D@WOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FKim Leadbeater, the MP who originally
OL,7,Fproposed the legislation, joined
OL,8,Fdemonstrators on Wednesday, and said
OL,9,Fit was "wrong, democratically and
OL,10,Fmorally, that the House of Lords have
OL,11,Ftalked the Bill out and allowed it to
OL,12,Ffall", after it twice passed votes in
OL,13,Fthe Commons, albeit with a narrower
OL,14,Fmajority the second time around.
OL,16,FPeers in the Lords have insisted they
OL,17,Fhave simply done their job of
OL,18,Fscrutinising legislation, which they
OL,19,Fargue is not safe.
OL,26,@qD@HOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
