OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FMs Wilcox said she had been left
OL,7,F"incredibly disappointed by some
OL,8,Fpeers", and offered to meet with
OL,9,FParalympian Baroness Tanni Grey-
OL,10,FThompson who has been a staunch
OL,11,Fopponent of the Bill.
OL,13,FShe said: "I really wish I could talk
OL,14,Fto her personally about this, and I
OL,15,Fwould always accept a conversation to
OL,16,Fhave a chat with her at any time and
OL,17,Fease her fears."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@FO]uD@KOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
