CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FBaroness Grey-Thompson has previously
OL,7,Fsaid she is not opposed to the
OL,8,Fprinciple of assisted dying but is
OL,9,Fagainst this Bill, saying she is
OL,10,Fworried about the particular
OL,11,Fvulnerabilities of disabled people and
OL,12,Fhas concerns about possible coercion
OL,13,Funder a Bill she said also
OL,14,F"fundamentally changes our
OL,15,Frelationship with medicine, with
OL,16,Fdoctors".
