PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FShe previously said her own experience
OL,7,Fwith her mother's difficult death with
OL,8,Fcancer means she understands people's
OL,9,Fstrong feelings, but insists there
OL,10,Fshould be more focus on improving end-
OL,11,Fof-life care.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's absolutely appalling
OL,14,Fthat people are scared about how
OL,15,Fthey're going to die. But we should be
OL,16,Fhaving proper specialist palliative
OL,17,Fcare."
OL,26,@uD@KOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
