PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776885106
OL,3,CDame Esther Rantzen's daughter
OL,4,C'furious' as assisted dying bill fails
OL,6,FWednesday's protest in favour of the
OL,7,Fbill was met with a counter
OL,8,Fdemonstration, held by people who were
OL,9,Fopposed to assisted dying.
OL,11,FAmanda Hunter, protesting for Together
OL,12,FDeclaration and Families Against
OL,13,FInvoluntary Medical Euthanasia, said:
OL,14,F"The Lords have not talked out this
OL,15,Fbill, they have talked some sense into
OL,16,Fit."
